## Next Steps for Deployment

Once deployed to Vercel, the analytics will automatically start tracking:
- Page views
- User sessions
- Navigation events

To enable Web Analytics on the Vercel dashboard:
1. Go to the project dashboard on Vercel
2. Navigate to the Analytics tab
3. Click "Enable" to activate Web Analytics
4. Deploy this update to production

After deployment, you should see a network request to `/_vercel/insights/view` in your browser's developer tools when visiting any page, confirming that analytics are working properly.
